message.body: Faye! (And Dan) I'm in love with the gift I received yesterday from you! Thank you both so much. Can't wait for June.
You are so welcome!!! Sorry I missed your call last night, I was at yoga then my phone was buried in my bag and on silent haha...glad you like the goodies!!
Any fun birthday plans other than conferences??
Just conferences right now! We will be back around 8pm Sunday so I will probably try to hop on some Cinco de mayo festivities. Do you have any big weekend plans?
Cinco de Mary!! We're actually up in PA, staying over at Dan's parents' tonight then getting the keys to our apt tmw and starting the move-in process. So, very low-key compared to last weekend hahaha
Awe that sounds so nice and relaxing. Have fun! And yes...it took me until mid week to feel normal after your party...the best!
Hahaha omg my voice wasn't back to normal until like yesterday...and on tues I went to yoga forgetting I still had a pen tattoo all over my back...oopsieee
Haha yes! I love it. Getting to know your friends was really nice and makes me more excited for the wedding.
